{"tid":2415276,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"世界級的防彈！BTS崛起傳奇4月搬大銀幕　最新預告曝光","createTime":"2021-02-20T06:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T10:47:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d97ff7809ecad7832b8f3302a5da376b27baa77","tid":2415276,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"紅遍全球的南韓天團「防彈少年團 BTS」，不只是K-POP的首席代表，進軍歐美有成的他們，讓不少國際巨星也爭相與他們合作，除此之外，BTS近年來更是獲得Billboard、葛萊美等知名音樂的獎項，而BTS的傳奇出道歷程，也將在今年4月以新的紀錄片形式電影上映，最新預告也搶先曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/20/3032983-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2F3032983-PH.jpg&h=dbdd6302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼韓國超人氣男團BTS。（圖／一念間電影提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/20/3032988-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2F3032988-PH.jpg&h=f8fce446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告一曝光，就能看到BTS不只跨足國際，目前已經成為大眾流行指標的他們也表示，其實剛出道的時候也沒有想這麼多，只是一群喜歡唱歌跳舞的大男孩，透過舞台去表達自己的想法，甚至是改變整個流行產業，然而這樣的成功並非偶然，BTS靠著獨特的音樂風格與啟發性的歌詞，不只啟發許多青少年族群的想法，甚至一度在聯合國上發表演說，也意味著BTS不只是一個偶像團體，而是相當有影響力的重要人物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/20/3032975-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F20%2F3032975-PH.jpg&h=41fc3630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓國人氣男團BTS新電影《崛起傳奇》即將上映。（圖／一念間電影提供）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ZOf5grIg-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2ZOf5grIg-U&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkiWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=cb8d9e7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ZOf5grIg-U</a><br />\n<br />\n在樂壇中獨樹一格的BTS，也已逐漸跳脫偶像的框架，成為一個擁有自己音樂風格的品牌，而2013年出道至今的他們今年也將成為9年差的藝人，也將透過紀錄片的方式述說他們一路走來的傳奇星路歷程，而BTS崛起傳奇電影預計將在4月正式上映。"},{"pid":"67fa5c2ea25e96334c5f99f2dfcbc3344c1bf7ec","tid":2415276,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"會唔會太勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4008ba62b28adaacbf7a01bb9b0b0098941901","tid":2415276,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"又bts...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4afe34393adaea603b7cd0e453d3293247af95","tid":2415276,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e4008ba62b28adaacbf7a01bb9b0b0098941901","tid":2415276,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"又bts...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:43:20.000Z","msg":"世界第1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215d1f3e2c43695a702dd659e2c88aff98ed1b84","tid":2415276,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e4afe34393adaea603b7cd0e453d3293247af95","tid":2415276,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e4008ba62b28adaacbf7a01bb9b0b0098941901","tid":2415276,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"又bts...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:43:20.000Z","msg":"世界第1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c9a4e03ffb5f01bcde875a84778373dd3a0